c: 9
v: 99
t: "“Ndipo alipo ena mwa Arabu a kuchimizi omwe akukhulupirira Allah ndi tsiku lachimaliziro ndipo zomwe akupereka (pa njira ya Allah) amazichita monga chodziyandikitsira nacho kwa Allah, ndi (chowachititsa kuti apeze) mapemphero a Mtumiki. Tamverani! Ndithu zimenezo ndizinthu zowayandikitsa kwa Allah. Allah adzawalowetsa ku Mtendere Wake. Ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"